// +------------------------------------------------------------+
// | purchase-create-batch.php                                  |
// +------------------------------------------------------------+

Description
-----------
Uploads a file containing purchase data for batch processing.

API URL
-------
http://www.crowdtwist.com/docs/api/end-point/purchase-create-batch

git URL
-------
git://github.com/CrowdTwist/php.git

Notes
-----
The sample code below assumes you executed the following to retrieve this
software:

    cd /opt
    mkdir crowdtwist
    cd crowdtwist
    git clone git://github.com/CrowdTwist/php.git

Sample CLI
----------
cd /opt/crowdtwist/php/bin/v1
php ./purchase-create-batch.php ...

Sample crontab
--------------
* * * * * (cd /opt/crowdtwist/php/bin/v1; php ./purchase-create-batch.php ...)

